e.<br/><br/>The Seller cannot be held liable for minor errors in photos or descriptions.</p><p>12.2. The Seller is not liable for losses or damages arising from delays caused by stock shortages.<br/><br/>Except in cases of fraud or willful misconduct, liability is limited to the value of the purchased Products.<br/><br/>The Seller is not liable for indirect damages.</p><h2><strong>13. Assignment</strong></h2><p>The Seller may assign its rights and obligations under the Sales Contract, including delivery, to third-party suppliers without affecting the Customer’s rights.</p><h2><strong>14. Force Majeure</strong></h2><p>The Seller is not liable for failure or delay in performing obligations due to events of force majeure.<br/><br/>In such cases, both parties may terminate the Sales Contract, without compensation.</p><h2><strong>15. Severability</strong></h2><p>If any provision is deemed invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions will continue in full force and effect.</p><h2><strong>16. Amendments</strong></h2><p>The Seller may amend these Terms at any time.<br/><br/>The version in force at the time of the order shall apply.</p><h2><strong>17. Applicable Law</strong></h2><p>These Terms and Conditions are governed by <strong>Italian law</strong>.<br/><br/>Any disputes arising from the Sales Contract shall be resolved in accordance with Italian legislation.</p>"
